  "keyFeatures": [
    "Interactive map creation and configuration",
    "Layer management with vector, raster, and live data sources",
    "Intelligent workflow automation triggered by spatial events",
    "Spatial data import/export supporting GeoJSON, Shapefile, CSV, KML",
